<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="ServicesInMyCity privacy policy (placeholder draft).">
  <section class="container" style="padding:48px 20px 64px; max-width:760px">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="disclaimer">Draft placeholder. This text has not been reviewed by counsel and is not yet a binding policy.</p>
    <p>ServicesInMyCity (a product of Elite Media Group) is designed to collect as little personal data as possible. In Phase 1 we do not offer accounts and do not require an email, password, or profile.</p>
    <h2>Anonymous sessions</h2>
    <p>We use an anonymous session identifier to keep a conversation continuous during your visit. It is not designed to identify you personally.</p>
    <h2>Consent</h2>
    <p>Optional features such as session memory or contributing anonymized aggregate signals require your explicit consent and can be declined without losing core functionality.</p>
    <h2>Third parties</h2>
    <p>We use Google for local business discovery and Anthropic to power Rocco. Requests to these services are made server-side. We use Google Analytics (GA4) for this site only.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about privacy can be directed to Elite Media Group.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
